 889:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   In Shutdown mode, the PLL, the HSI, the LSI and the HSE oscillators are switched
 890:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         off. The voltage regulator is disabled and Vcore domain is powered off.
 891:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         SRAM and registers contents are lost except for registers in the Backup domain.
 892:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         The BOR is not available.
 893:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   The I/Os can be configured either with a pull-up or pull-down or can
 894:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         be kept in analog state.
 895:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullUp() and HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullDown()
 896:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         respectively enable Pull Up and PullDown state.
 897:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         HAL_PWREx_DisableGPIOPullUp() & HAL_PWREx_DisableGPIOPullDown()
 898:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         disable the same. These states are effective in Standby mode only if
